name: access-zone-occupancy-state
description: Enumerated values representing the occupancy state of an access zone relative to its limits.

values.name: below-lower-limit
values.description: Zone occupancy is below the lower limit.

values.name: at-lower-limit
values.description: Zone occupancy is at the lower limit.

values.name: at-upper-limit
values.description: Zone occupancy is at the upper limit.

values.name: above-upper-limit
values.description: Zone occupancy is above the upper limit.
